2. Mouse Actions
left_click

Inputs:
x: X-coordinate of the click.
y: Y-coordinate of the click.
right_click, middle_click

Inputs:
x: X-coordinate.
y: Y-coordinate.
double_left_click

Inputs:
x: X-coordinate.
y: Y-coordinate.
mouse_drag

Inputs:
start_x, start_y: Start coordinates.
end_x, end_y: End coordinates.
duration: Time for the drag (default: 1.0).
mouse_hover

Inputs:
x, y: Coordinates to hover over.
duration: Duration of hover (default: 1.0).
mouse_scroll

Inputs:
direction: "up" or "down" (default: "up").
amount: Scroll amount (default: 1).
mouse_move

Inputs:
x, y: Target coordinates.
duration: Duration for movement (default: 0.5).
context_menu_open

Inputs:
x, y: Coordinates to open the context menu.
3. Keyboard Actions
keystroke

Inputs:
key: The key to press.
key_combination

Inputs:
keys: List of keys to press simultaneously.
typing_sequence

Inputs:
text: String to type.
typingSpeed: Delay between keystrokes (default: 0.1).
special_key_press

Inputs:
key: The special key to press (e.g., "Ctrl").
shortcut_use

Inputs:
shortcut: A predefined keyboard shortcut.
4. File and Folder Actions
file_open, file_save

Inputs:
file_path: Path to the file.
For file_save: content: Data to save.
file_delete

Inputs:
file_path: Path to the file.
file_rename

Inputs:
file_path: Original file path.
new_name: New name for the file.
file_move, file_copy

Inputs:
file_path: Source file path.
destination_path: Destination path.
file_upload

Inputs:
file_path: File to upload.
file_download

Inputs:
file_url: URL of the file.
destination_path: Local path to save the file.
5. Browser Actions
open_selenium

Inputs:
browser: Browser type ("chrome", "firefox", etc., default: "chrome").
headless: Boolean for headless mode (default: False).
close_selenium

Inputs: None.
element_interact

Inputs:
selector: CSS selector or other identifier.
by: Selector strategy (default: By.CSS_SELECTOR).
url_navigation

Inputs:
url: Target URL.
search_query

Inputs:
query: Search query text.
wait_time: Time to wait for results (default: 2).
6. Communication Actions
email_read

Inputs:
platform: Email platform (default: "outlook").
criteria: Search or filter criteria.
email_write

Inputs:
platform: Email platform (default: "outlook").
to: Recipient email.
subject, body: Email content.
cc, bcc: Optional CC/BCC recipients.
email_send

Inputs:
to_address, subject, body: Email details.
smtp_server, smtp_port: SMTP settings.
smtp_username, smtp_password: Authentication credentials.
scan_inbox, email_search

Inputs:
criteria: Search/filter criteria.
platform: Email platform (default: "outlook").
7. Security and Authentication Actions
login_attempt

Inputs:
name: Credential name.
logout

Inputs: None.
permission_request

Inputs:
permission: Specific permission requested.
run_as_administrator

Inputs:
command: Command to execute with elevated privileges.
8. Specialized Actions
dropdown_select

Inputs:
selector: Dropdown selector.
value: Option to select.
by: Selector strategy (default: By.CSS_SELECTOR).
is_local: Boolean for local dropdowns (default: False).
window_title: Title of the application (for local dropdowns).
wait

Inputs:
duration: Wait duration (default: 1).
wait_for

Inputs:
condition: Condition to wait for.
selector: Target element's selector.
timeout: Timeout duration (default: 30).
by: Selector strategy (default: By.CSS_SELECTOR).